{"in": {"lines": ["TITLE: The Legend of Fangs the Fearless: Scene 2.0", "SCENE: https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/fangs/1/back-alley-raining-2m.mp3 (no wait)", "SCENE: A dark back-alley. Night.", "FANGS: (loud) OK. WHAT DO WE DO NOW?", "PEONY: Sshhh... (pause) (pause) (pause)", "FANGS: (whisper) ok. What do we do now?", "PEONY: (soft) You don't have to whisper. Just don't shout. That's all. We wait.", "FANGS: Wait?", "PEONY: Yes. We wait for Yu Hu the wise.", "FANGS: Who?", "PEONY: No. Yu Hu. You have to pronounce the \"Yu\"", "FANGS: U?", "PEONY: No. You.", "FANGS: Oh! Yu.", "PEONY: No. Just \"Yu\"", "FANGS: Yes.", "PEONY: No. Only rounded vowels, palatal glides and voiceless glottal fricatives. No sibilants.", "FANGS: I get it now! Yoo hoo!", "PEONY: No. Not \"Yoo hoo\". \"Yu Hu\". She doesn't like two vowels in a row.", "FANGS: Boy. She sounds real picky if you ask me.", "PEONY: And oh, the vowels and consonants have to alternate.", "FANGS: So Y is a consonant?", "PEONY: Yes.", "FANGS: No. Not S. Y.", "PEONY: Yes. Y. Why not?", "FANGS: Y-nought? As in ground level?", "PEONY: No. \"Why not\", as in Converse Analysis.", "FANGS: But... why not what?", "SCENE: https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/fangs/1/owl-hoots-23s.mp3 (no wait)", "SCENE: (pause) (pause)", "PEONY: Shhh... Do you hear that? (pause)", "FANGS: Hear what? (pause)", "PEONY: Listen...&nbsp;(pause)", "SCENE: https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/fangs/1/bird-flying-in-fluttering-flying-away-255s.mp3 (no wait)", "SCENE: https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/misc/silence-5s.mp3", "FANGS: What  (pause) (pause)", "PEONY: (whisper) Sshhh. See if you can hear her name (pause)", "SCENE: https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/fangs/1/owl-hoots-23s.mp3 (no wait)", "SCENE: https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/misc/silence-5s.mp3", "PEONY: Ah. That's Yu Hu, alright.", "FANGS: Wait! Yu Hu's an owl?", "PEONY: Yes, Fangs. Does that matter?", "FANGS: Not to me. No. But don't the likes of them eat the likes of you?", "PEONY: Oh, that? Not to worry. Yu Hu only eats mice that want to be eaten.", "FANGS: And you don't want to be eaten, I presume?", "PEONY: I don't mind, really. But I can see a time when I'd want it.", "FANGS: I'll never understand you, Peony!", "PEONY: It doesn't matter, Fangs. Just understand Yu Hu.", "FANGS: Who? You?", "PEONY: No. Not me. You.", "FANGS: Oh.", "PEONY: Yes. You.", "FANGS: Well, is Yu Hu ever going to land or is she going to keep hovering above us like that? It's driving me dizzy.", "PEONY: Oh. Yu Hu never lands. She's always high.", "FANGS: Are you kidding? How do we get to talk to her?", "PEONY: Well, obviously one of us has to go up there.", "FANGS: Who? You?", "PEONY: No. Not me. I'm afraid of heights.", "SCENE: https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/fangs/1/back-alley-raining-2m.mp3 (no wait)", "FANGS: Are you out of your mind, Peony? Look at how big I am? Do you honestly think I'm going to try and fly?", "PEONY: Ah. You don't have to try, Fangs. I have just the thing.", "FANGS: Sure. If you have any brilliant ideas for getting me up there, I'm all ears.", "PEONY: As a matter of fact, I do. (pause)", "SCENE: https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/misc/random-foley-2s.mp3", "PEONY: Ta-daaa! (pause) (pause)", "FANGS: Lollipops? Isn't it too early to be celebrating?", "PEONY: No, Fangs. This is what you need. Just the thing. Let me just make sure... Luminare's Levitating, Luminare's Levitating Leviathan Leadenboot - oops not this one. Let's see, two more. Ok.", "FANGS: (slow) Lollipops?", "PEONY: Not just any lollipops, Fangs. These are from Luminare's floating castle. See. It says so on the wrapper.", "FANGS: Let me see.", "PEONY: Here. We have Fo...", "FANGS: Yummy. These look delicious.", "PEONY: NO, FANGS, NO!!!", "NARRATOR: Fangs starts crunching into a lollipop.", "PEONY: We should have saved them all for later!&nbsp;", "SCENE: https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/fangs/1/crunchy-eating-14s.mp3", "PEONY: Well! Now we have three. Each of these can keep you afloat for a little time.", "FANGS: A little ay? Well, how much?", "PEONY: Dunno, Fangs. How much did you swallow? (pause) (pause)", "FANGS: (high) Whoo! What's happening? I feel light headed all of a sudden.", "PEONY: Oh. That would be the Levitating lollipops at work. Just let them do their job, Fangs. Feel light bodied. And here, hold on to these three other lollipops.", "NARRATOR: Fangs begins to float up until he reaches the center of Yu Hu's orbit.", "YU HU: You who has summoned me, speak your mind. Open your heart, Yu Hu then will feel your soul. I'll tell its darkness to depart.", "FANGS: (slow) Err. Yu Hu. It's not quite as dire as you make it out.", "YU HU: You who dares to question Yu Hu?", "NARRATOR: Suddenly Fangs starts to fall. In a panic, he jams the remaining lollipops in his mouth just in time.", "SCENE: https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/fangs/1/fast-crunchy-eating-4s.mp3", "NARRATOR: He falls low enough to hear Peony, but not hit the ground.", "PEONY: Don't waste time with small talk, Fangs. You only have a little time up there. Tell her you want to sleep.", "NARRATOR: Fangs floats up again to meet Yu Hu.", "FANGS: Yu Hu, I just want to sleep. That's all.", "YU HU: You who seeks to sleep... Snoozlestown is where... the gods return to weep... for those who do not share.", "NARRATOR: Fangs is starting to feel heavy again.", "FANGS: (fast). Yu Hu, I'm sorry about the rush. But I'm not one for riddles. Can you please tell me the answer straight up? I'm the one who needs to sleep. Not you.", "YU HU: (slow). Yes. You who wants to sleep, whose dreams are all a'broken. Yu Hu tries to keep, the words that she has spoken.", "FANGS: (fast) Wait... Wait. I'm not quite sure we're communicating. Hey Yu, where are you going?", "YU HU: Farewell, Tiger, burning bright. The Chrysalis will set you right.", "FANGS: A Chrysalis? What is that?", "YU HU: A Chrysalis. A new beginning. Reprisal is... The old way.", "FANGS: What? And where's your rhyme, when you're stretched for time?", "YU HU: Good luck, Fangs.", "SCENE: https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/fangs/1/bird-flying-away-4s.mp3", "NARRATOR: Yu Hu flies away. And Fangs comes crashing down on a bunch of garbage cans.", "SCENE: https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/fangs/1/double-thud-2s.mp3", "FANGS: Ow! Ow! Ow! Ouch! (pause) (pause)", "PEONY: Ah Fangs, I never had a chance to show you how to land safely with these lollipops.", "FANGS: You mean you've used them?", "PEONY: Sure I have.", "FANGS: But I thought you were afraid of heights.", "PEONY: Yes, but not if I have these lollipops.", "FANGS: Now she tells me!", "PEONY: Well, what did she tell you?", "FANGS: I don't know Peony. Maybe you should have gone instead. You seem to be able to understand Yu Hu.", "PEONY: Never mind that, Fangs. What did she tell you?", "FANGS: A whole lot of rubbish. That's what she told me. Where is Snoozlestown?", "PEONY: Snoozlestown? I'm surprised?", "FANGS: Why? Snoozlestown seems like the perfect place to find Snoozlestones.", "PEONY: No. There are no Snoozlestones in Snoozletown. Maybe there once was. But not any more.", "FANGS: Huh? So why did Yu Tell us to go there?", "PEONY: Who? Me?", "FANGS: No. Yu.", "PEONY: Dunno Fangs. What else did she say?", "FANGS: Something about a crisis...", "PEONY: Crisis? Are you sure?", "FANGS: Yeah. Crisis of new beginnings or some hokey thing like that.", "PEONY: Ah, yes! That must be the Chrysalis.", "FANGS: Yeah! Chrysalis.", "PEONY: There's something called Pure Panacea. It gives you a new beginning. Maybe the Chrysalis has something to do with it. Legend has it that it sends you into a cocoon and when you come out of it, you'll have everything you want.", "FANGS: Panacea? What's that? Will it help me sleep?", "PEONY: It's a wildcard, Fangs. It can be used for anything. But it can only be collected in Snoozestown. Maybe that's why she wants us to go there.", "FANGS: Boy! This is getting weirder by the hour. Is this all for real? Nothing seems simple anymore.", "PEONY: What are you saying, Fangs? Do you wish you had never come?", "FANGS: It sure is starting to feel like that. But let's go to this blasted Snoozlestown and get this over with.", "PEONY: Yes, Fangs. Let's go.", "SCENE: https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/fangs/1/footsteps-receding-10s.mp3 (no wait)", "SCENE: https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/misc/silence-5s.mp3", "SCENE: https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/fangs/1/brian-fangs-crazy-cookie-fade-out.mp3"], "title": "Questing Lores", "subtitle": "<span id=\"tr_lore_id\">the legend of fangs - scene 2.0</span>", "speaker_map": {"SCENE": "Joanna", "TITLE": "Joanna", "FANGS": "Brian", "PEONY": "Raveena", "NARRATOR": "Matthew", "YU HU": "Aditi", "[object HTMLTableCellElement]": "Joanna"}}, "out": {"cache_id": "aba8be75b4342e9051f1f5fbd56ad03f", "audio_objects": [["d9ee3a1c8863b5ebf0618340cbd45d89-the-legend-of-fangs-the-f---", 0], ["https://quests.nonlinearmedia.org/lores/res/mp3/fangs/1/back-alley-raining-2m.mp3", 1], ["0936d8dec1da680fa2baee0afd812398-a-dark-back-alley--night-", 0], ["6dc0d335ed2aaf341effc763ed35f842--ok--what-do-we-do-now-", 0], ["825ec6352222aa0d83f3143f39b77654-sshhh------", 0], ["a7b3679d7b724a6e4f4eb68f24896c33--ok--what-do-we-do-now-", 0], ["c9536e3a9247e8d20bffe4c62b442783--you-don-t-have-to-whispe---", 0], ["4d527d06009e5de6aa6248acf8016d08-wait-", 0], ["956d41dc8960bd24a17962f526918e71-yes--we-wait-for-yu-hu-th---", 0], ["bc822491be81234c9da9df2c39382c95-who-", 0], ["ec808e54c678f111e3f3c31820f1cc92-no--yu-hu--you-have-to-pr---", 0], ["50f6972d1a10c425c1676367bc5ff7f5-u-", 0], ["738d2a861249b5caf59c58b8546c7d17-no--you-", 0], ["5b569ec1350d9fac0b20d8f5f6ee7e0e-oh--yu-", 0], ["525ce754cf46f1ff11f7dabe93eeba20-no--just--yu-", 0], ["1ff84bae3c9c65d498efc507c43517b1-yes-", 0], ["f7d61e6755368f5de4daa39e39a0